# Build determinism ---------------------------------------------------------
# The datafile packer (src/bme/datafile.c) reads these inputs in BINARY mode,
# so their bytes must be identical on every OS. Force LF regardless of the
# contributor's platform or core.autocrlf setting; otherwise a Windows checkout
# would pack CRLF and change the generated src/goatdata.c (and thus the embedded
# player). See tests/docs/build-determinism.md.
*.s     text eol=lf
*.seq   text eol=lf
*.gtp   text eol=lf

# Packed binary resources: never apply text/EOL conversion.
*.bin   binary
*.bmp   binary
*.png   binary

# Binary fixtures / tool outputs.
*.sng   binary
*.prg   binary
*.sid   binary
*.dat   binary
